    ""

translate ru JustBeforeBattleOfRahayal_145e87c2:
    # "She could imagine it almost peaceful."
    ""

translate ru JustBeforeBattleOfRahayal_bbdc41b0:
    # "But she had seen how quickly things could change."
    ""

translate ru JustBeforeBattleOfRahayal_8e33ab85:
    # "Whatever would come..."
    ""

translate ru JustBeforeBattleOfRahayal_cfdfdb2b:
    # "She would be ready."
    ""

translate ru JustBeforeBattleOfRahayal_7789c49f:
    # "Then, just as she felt as if she had convinced herself of her bravery, she watched she sky above her warp and twist."
    ""

translate ru JustBeforeBattleOfRahayal_d2484528:
    # "Sarah saw a great rift tear through the heavens."
    ""

translate ru JustBeforeBattleOfRahayal_8dea7334:
    # "And as reality itself tore apart, she saw the countless white masks of the beasts emerge."
    ""

